txt.en: 'The Web-wife has greater plans for us, my young ones'
'Our numbers are needed, so we will leave this place and continue to await orders from the Web-wife'
'But we will not leave this intruder empty-handed....'
'There is no sign of Vaskorn yet, he must be held captive in the heart of the Ungoledain encampment'
'The clanking of weapons and yelling of orders is much more audible. It appears the Ungoledain forces are ready for you'
'Why did she not call us to her?'
'There is a captured Beorning up ahead, it must be Vaskorn!'
'You are not worthy of testing my skills. You will face my pet instead!'
'You may have taken Old Mother from us, but you shall never have the Web-wife'
'We are her chosen guardians and we will worship her!'
'Deeper, deeper into our web you come'
